Paper: hep-th/9911154

Date: 1999-11-19

Title: PhreMology--calibrating M-branes

Authors: P.K. Townsend

Comments: 13 pp. Strings '99 contribution. Various points corrected

Journal-ref: Class.Quant.Grav. 17 (2000) 1267-1276

The relevance of calibrations, and `generalized' calibrations, tosupersymmetric M-brane configurations, and their associated field theories, isreviewed, with emphasis on applications to domain walls and domain walljunctions of D=4 N=1 supersymmetric field theories.